original_title: Girls' Night Out: Superstar Women of Country
overview: Fundraising concert starring Rascal Flatts, John Foggerty, Little Big Town, Ronnie Dunn, Blake Shelton and Vince Gill.  The night's honorees included Reba, The Judds, Miranda Lambert, Loretta Lynn, Martina McBride, Jennifer Nettles of Sugarland, and Carrie Underwood.
title: Girls' Night Out: Superstar Women of Country
